page.title: 13JUNIOR SCHOOL GIRL
page.content: I am a{Brownie.}I go to Brownies every Tuesday .On a Wednesday I go to Gym. On a Thursday I go{swimming}at half past seven,until half past eight.Life around where I live can be quite boring some times I cannot find anyone to{play}with.Sometimes I phone my friend Vicki. We take these two dogs called Muffin and Poppy for a walk. We play with them in the back garden. My sister, Vicki,and I are usually playing a game called Cluedo.My sister is called Andrea,she is two years ahead of me at school. I am in form E Mrs Mc.Grath is my teacher,my favourite{food}is Burger and Chips from the Fish and Chip shop.My favourite pop group is WHAM,my room is covered in posters of them.My favourite programme is Tom and Jerry.My name is Christina and I am nine.
